set number
set wrapmargin=4

" Is this a thing?:
set encoding=utf-8

nnoremap <c-d> dd
inoremap <c-d> <esc>ddi
inoremap <c-l> <esc><c-l>i
inoremap jk <esc>
inoremap <c-u> <esc>viwU<esc>i
nnoremap <c-u> viwU<esc>

" Whitespace stuff
" Default vim settings (?):
" set tabstop=8 softtabstop=8 shiftwidth=8 noexpandtab
set tabstop=4
set shiftwidth=4
set softtabstop=4
set noexpandtab